</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【CES 2022】NVIDIA RTX 3090 Ti 發佈，頂級顯示卡詳細規格</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/05/nvidia-announces-rtx-3090-ti-with-faster-memory-and-performance/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=nvidia-announces-rtx-3090-ti-with-faster-memory-and-performance</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jan 2022 12:57:02 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[CES 2022]]></category><category><![CDATA[GeForce RTX 3050]]></category><category><![CDATA[GeForce RTX 3090 Ti]]></category><category><![CDATA[NVIDIA]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1079794</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>NVIDIA 早前於 CES 2022 上發佈多項新產品，當中包括全新入門級的 GeForce RTX 305 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">NVIDIA 早前於 CES 2022 上發佈多項新產品，當中包括全新入門級的 GeForce RTX 3050；又預告 NVIDIA 將推出新一代採用「Ampere」架構的「GeForce RTX 30」系列最頂級的顯示卡「GeForce RTX 3090 Ti」，預計將在本月內正式推出。</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/every-new-graphics-card-announced-at-ces-2022_wp8f.jpg.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079811" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/every-new-graphics-card-announced-at-ces-2022_wp8f.jpg-694x364.png" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/every-new-graphics-card-announced-at-ces-2022_wp8f.jpg-694x364.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/every-new-graphics-card-announced-at-ces-2022_wp8f.jpg-1280x671.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/every-new-graphics-card-announced-at-ces-2022_wp8f.jpg-768x402.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/every-new-graphics-card-announced-at-ces-2022_wp8f.jpg-1536x805.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/every-new-graphics-card-announced-at-ces-2022_wp8f.jpg-2048x1073.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/every-new-graphics-card-announced-at-ces-2022_wp8f.jpg.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">新推出的 GeForce RTX 3050 配備第三代的 Tensor 核心，具有 8GB GDDR6 記憶體，具備光線追蹤、DLSS 等先進功能，可提供每秒 9 兆次著色器 / 18 兆次光線追蹤 / 73 兆次 Tensor 運算效能。預計將取代 GeForce GTX 1650 的主流定位，讓新一代遊戲在 1440p 開啟光線追蹤的設定下，達成 60FPS 以上的畫面輸出。GeForce RTX 3050 預計於 1 月 27 日正式推出，定價為 US$249 (約港幣 1942 元)。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1079803" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/nvidia-ces-2022-rtx-3050-d-large-3840-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/nvidia-ces-2022-rtx-3050-d-large-3840-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/nvidia-ces-2022-rtx-3050-d-large-3840-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/nvidia-ces-2022-rtx-3050-d-large-3840-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/nvidia-ces-2022-rtx-3050-d-large-3840-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/nvidia-ces-2022-rtx-3050-d-large-3840-2048x1152.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/nvidia-ces-2022-rtx-3050-d-large-3840.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">預告將推出的 GeForce RTX 3090 Ti 則配備 24GB GDDR6X 記憶體，傳輸速度提升至 21Gbps，可提供每秒 40 兆次著色器運算、78 兆次光線追蹤運算、320 兆次 Tensor 運算的處理效能，更能加強 AI 運算和渲染輸出的速度。但 GeForce RTX 3090 Ti 的供電規格、上市日期與價格等詳情仍未有確實消息，有待官方後續公佈。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_63240"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6KoscQVKpAQ?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.nvidia.cn/geforce/news/nvidia-geforce-rtx-ces-2022-announcements/">NVIDIA</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
