dn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.34.34-2048x1133.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.34.34.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.33.39.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079692" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.33.39-694x384.png" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.33.39-694x384.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.33.39-1280x708.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.33.39-768x425.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.33.39-1536x849.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.33.39-2048x1132.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.33.39.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.34.49.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1079693" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.34.49-694x385.png" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.34.49-694x385.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.34.49-1280x710.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.34.49-768x426.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.34.49-1536x852.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.34.49-2048x1136.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-05-14.34.49.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在比較影片的推文下，有不少中國玩家分別以中文、英文和日文道歉，同時也狠批「完美世界」行為丟臉，破壞了中國人的聲譽。不過，「Hurrary!」代表強調，並沒對特定國家抱負面觀感，雖片段由中國公司抄襲製作，但同時亦是一位中國網友禮貌地告知，希望大家從「國家」角度討論此事。</p></div><div class="css-kl86x4">資料來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/POPREQ/status/1476441690294874119?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1476441690294874119%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-admin%2Fpost.php%3Fpost%3D1079684action%3Deditclassic-editor">Twitter</a></div><div class="css-kl86x4">—</div><div class="css-16zmdoi" data-is-focusable="true">unwire.hk Mewe 專頁：<a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></div></p><div class="feedflare">
