</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【CES 2022】ASUS ROG Zephyrus Duo 16 雙芒筆電，新設計主副螢幕無縫銜接</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/05/rog-zephyrus-duo-16-2022-gx650/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=rog-zephyrus-duo-16-2022-gx650</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jan 2022 10:06:12 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[asus]]></category><category><![CDATA[CES 2022]]></category><category><![CDATA[ROG]]></category><category><![CDATA[ROG Zephyrus Duo 16]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1079744</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>ROG 早前於 CES 期間舉行《For Those Who Dare: The Rise of Gamers [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">ROG 早前於 CES 期間舉行《For Those Who Dare: The Rise of Gamers》線上發表會，發表了一連串電競的新產品。當中的 </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ROG Zephyrus Duo 16 作為 ROG 2022 旗艦產品，受到高度關注。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1079752" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.38.01-694x342.png" alt="" width="694" height="342" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.38.01-694x342.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.38.01-1280x630.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.38.01-768x378.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.38.01-1536x756.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.38.01-2048x1008.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.38.01.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">ROG Zephyrus Duo 16 機身尺寸比前代 15 吋更小，卻搭載了更大的 16 吋螢幕，另外還有第二螢幕 ScreenPad Plus。在用家掀開電腦時，第二螢幕將透過全新四向螢幕轉軸抬升並向後滑動，無縫銜接主螢幕，無論在視覺還是實體上，主螢幕及第二螢幕的連貫性無疑是目前所有 Duo 筆記型電腦當中最高的一個。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1079746" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.25.40-694x280.png" alt="" width="694" height="280" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.25.40-694x280.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.25.40-1280x516.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.25.40-768x309.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.25.40-1536x619.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.25.40-2048x825.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.25.40.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1079747" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.26.31-694x308.png" alt="" width="694" height="308" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.26.31-694x308.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.26.31-1280x568.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.26.31-768x341.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.26.31-1536x682.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.26.31-2048x910.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.26.31.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">在主螢幕方面，ROG Zephyrus Duo 16 提供兩款選擇：包括全新 ROG Nebula HDR 螢幕，採用 QHD、16:10 mini-LED 面板，擁有 165Hz 更新率並通過 VESA DisplayHDR 1000 認證，對比度達 100,000:1；或是與 BOE 合作開發的獨家螢幕 Dual Spec，可切換 4K 120Hz 或 Full HD 240Hz，自由控制解析度與螢幕更新率。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1079748" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.27.08-694x227.png" alt="" width="694" height="227" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.27.08-694x227.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.27.08-1280x420.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.27.08-768x252.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.27.08-1536x503.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.27.08-2048x671.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.27.08.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">ROG Zephyrus Duo 16 在規格上亦相當出色，最高搭載 AMD Ryzen 9 6000 系列處理器與 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3080Ti 顯示卡；升級的液態金屬散熱技術，最高可使處理器降低 15°C；第二螢幕抬升後的 Active Aerodynamic System Plus（AAS+）2.0 散熱系統，進氣口增加 30% 氣流，幫助維持低溫；支援獨顯直連的功能，意即獨顯（dGPU）訊號直接輸出，不用繞道內顯（iGPU），以減少畫面延遲，對於遊戲幀數也能大幅增加。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1079749" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.25.11-694x282.png" alt="" width="694" height="282" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.25.11-694x282.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.25.11-1280x519.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.25.11-768x312.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.25.11-1536x623.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.25.11-2048x831.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕快照-2022-01-05-下午 4.25.11.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://rog.asus.com/laptops/rog-zephyrus/rog-zephyrus-duo-16-2022-series/">ROG</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
